Mpiima Dorothy Christine (amụrụ na 22 Julaị 1959) bụ onye omeiwu Ugandan nke jere ozi na omeiwu nke itoolu nke Uganda Ọ bụ onye nnọchi anya otu ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị nke National Resistance Movement nke Buikwe District.

Na omeiwu nke itoolu, ọ bụ onye omeiwu maka Buikwe District. Christine Kasule Mugerwa tinyere akwụkwọ mkpesa megide Mpiima Dorothy na-ajụ iru eru agụmakwụkwọ ya na maka ịgha ụgha n'oge mkpọsa ya na iri ngo maka ndị na-atụ vootu. Mgbe Kasule gosipụtaraghị ugboro atọ, onye bụbu onye isi ikpe, Justice Monica Mugenyi jụrụ akwụkwọ mkpesa ahụ. Otú ọ dị, ụlọ ikpe dị elu na Jinja mechara weghachite mkpesa ahụ a jụrụ.

N'afọ 2016, Judith Babirye tụfuru oche ya na Nzukọ nke iri. Ọ bụ onye nkuzi nwere diplọma tupu ọ banye na Nzukọ Ndị Omeiwu. Christine so na ndị a họpụtara National Resistance Movement Candidates na 2020 Primaries on the Electoral Commission wepụtara ndepụta.
